arts.ttl: Ihattaren earns RKC a point at Heerenveen
arts.sum: Mohammed Ihattaren’s last-minute penalty earned RKC Waalwijk a 1-1 draw at Heerenveen. With the first big chance of the game, Heerenveen took the lead with Levi Sman stabbing in a cross from Jacob Trenskow. Heerenveen then had to replace Trenskow, who picked up an ankle injury.
